## Bottom Line

> **Any code that is deliberately obfuscated to this degree in a production environment should be treated as potentially hostile until fully deobfuscated and audited.** Legitimate physics simulations do not require string encoding, control flow flattening, or variable mangling. Either obtain the original source code or replace it entirely.
